00:24:14.830 --> 00:24:16.640 align:middle line:90%
Be aware of that.

00:24:16.640 --> 00:24:19.720 align:middle line:84%
I have a very young body,
which likes to eat also.

00:24:19.720 --> 00:24:24.120 align:middle line:90%


00:24:24.120 --> 00:24:26.950 align:middle line:84%
I'm eating the
same thing you are.

00:24:26.950 --> 00:24:27.750 align:middle line:90%
So grow up.

00:24:27.750 --> 00:24:34.040 align:middle line:90%


00:24:34.040 --> 00:24:38.060 align:middle line:84%
We are on a spiritual journey,
and I want spirituality

00:24:38.060 --> 00:24:41.240 align:middle line:84%
only till it comes in
package, in the box I want.

00:24:41.240 --> 00:24:43.810 align:middle line:90%


