It's not Costco.

00:24:45.020 --> 00:24:49.960 align:middle line:84%
We are not at Costco
or Barneys or Nordstrom

00:24:49.960 --> 00:24:52.150 align:middle line:90%
or any shopping mall, all right?

00:24:52.150 --> 00:24:57.750 align:middle line:84%
We are on a journey
of transformation.

00:24:57.750 --> 00:25:03.580 align:middle line:84%
Every little opportunity
I'll take to test you.

00:25:03.580 --> 00:25:07.510 align:middle line:90%


00:25:07.510 --> 00:25:10.540 align:middle line:84%
We'll do the teaching, and then
within the next hour or two,

00:25:10.540 --> 00:25:13.450 align:middle line:84%
you will get the opportunity
to practice the teaching.

00:25:13.450 --> 00:25:17.510 align:middle line:84%
Otherwise, we can sit and all we
can do is I can keep teaching.

00:25:17.510 --> 00:25:18.310 align:middle line:90%
Do you understand?

00:25:18.310 --> 00:25:20.200 align:middle line:84%
And we can keep
reading from scriptures

00:25:20.200 --> 00:25:22.690 align:middle line:84%
and I can talk about
transcendental reality and all

00:25:22.690 --> 00:25:23.490 align:middle line:90%
of that.

00:25:23.490 --> 00:25:24.310 align:middle line:90%
And you say, wow.

00:25:24.310 --> 00:25:25.110 align:middle line:90%
All of that.

00:25:25.110 --> 00:25:26.453 align:middle line:90%
And then what alters?

00:25:26.453 --> 00:25:27.370 align:middle line:90%
We are still the same.

00:25:27.370 --> 00:25:29.470 align:middle line:90%
Just new vocabulary.

00:25:29.470 --> 00:25:31.660 align:middle line:90%
New information in the mind.

00:25:31.660 --> 00:25:34.030 align:middle line:90%
Nothing within us has altered.

00:25:34.030 --> 00:25:35.380 align:middle line:90%
We are the same people.

00:25:35.380 --> 00:25:37.980 align:middle line:84%
Magic will only happen
outside of your comfort zone.

00:25:37.980 --> 00:25:40.500 align:middle line:90%


00:25:40.500 --> 00:25:42.990 align:middle line:84%
Somebody said to me,
oh, I was expecting

00:25:42.990 --> 00:25:44.030 align:middle line:90%
we would do more yoga.

00:25:44.030 --> 00:25:47.240 align:middle line:90%


00:25:47.240 --> 00:25:50.030 align:middle line:90%
This is yoga.

00:25:50.030 --> 00:25:51.610 align:middle line:90%
Yoga is [NON-ENGLISH].

00:25:51.610 --> 00:25:53.960 align:middle line:90%
The sensation of self is yoga.

00:25:53.960 --> 00:25:55.610 align:middle line:84%
The transcendence
of self is yoga,

00:25:55.610 --> 00:25:59.830 align:middle line:84%
towards transcendence of
the mind, its reactions,

00:25:59.830 --> 00:26:04.955 align:middle line:84%
its calculations, its
agendas, its expectations.

00:26:04.955 --> 00:26:06.580 align:middle line:84%
The conditioned self,
the transcendence

00:26:06.580 --> 00:26:09.910 align:middle line:84%
of the conditioned self
is the beginning of yoga.

00:26:09.910 --> 00:26:13.050 align:middle line:90%
Not the stretching.

00:26:13.050 --> 00:26:14.300 align:middle line:90%
That's just called stretching.

00:26:14.300 --> 00:26:15.445 align:middle line:90%
Don't call it yoga.

00:26:15.445 --> 00:26:19.070 align:middle line:90%
Call it stretching.

00:26:19.070 --> 00:26:20.820 align:middle line:84%
Some will be triggered
by something.

00:26:20.820 --> 00:26:22.070 align:middle line:90%
Some others will be triggered.

00:26:22.070 --> 00:26:27.320 align:middle line:84%
Not one thing will
trigger everybody, right?

00:26:27.320 --> 00:26:30.740 align:middle line:90%
None of it is personal.

00:26:30.740 --> 00:26:34.130 align:middle line:84%
But these are
opportunities to practice,

00:26:34.130 --> 00:26:36.530 align:middle line:84%
to really look at self,
that at, how does self

00:26:36.530 --> 00:26:37.700 align:middle line:90%
react at these moments?

00:26:37.700 --> 00:26:46.540 align:middle line:90%


00:26:46.540 --> 00:26:49.810 align:middle line:84%
This is not a journey to feel
better, do you understand?

00:26:49.810 --> 00:26:52.450 align:middle line:90%
You come here to transcend.

00:26:52.450 --> 00:26:56.530 align:middle line:84%
We come here to expand,
not just to put Band-Aids.

00:26:56.530 --> 00:26:59.510 align:middle line:90%


00:26:59.510 --> 00:27:03.110 align:middle line:90%
We come here to go deeper.

00:27:03.110 --> 00:27:04.340 align:middle line:90%
And that's what we test.

00:27:04.340 --> 00:27:06.260 align:middle line:90%
What if our attention is taken?

00:27:06.260 --> 00:27:07.400 align:middle line:90%
What takes our attention?

00:27:07.400 --> 00:27:09.192 align:middle line:84%
When we get up, as we
sit around the table,

00:27:09.192 --> 00:27:15.780 align:middle line:84%
what do we talk
about in those gaps?

00:27:15.780 --> 00:27:18.800 align:middle line:90%
What are our conversations?

00:27:18.800 --> 00:27:20.300 align:middle line:84%
What are we giving
our attention to?

00:27:20.300 --> 00:27:25.230 align:middle line:90%


00:27:25.230 --> 00:27:31.245 align:middle line:90%
Gossiping, cribbing, grouping.

00:27:31.245 --> 00:27:35.520 align:middle line:90%


00:27:35.520 --> 00:27:38.520 align:middle line:84%
It's life at play,
right here, right now.

00:27:38.520 --> 00:27:40.350 align:middle line:84%
And that's where
we get to practice,

00:27:40.350 --> 00:27:41.558 align:middle line:90%
because there is no escaping.

00:27:41.558 --> 00:27:44.100 align:middle line:90%


00:27:44.100 --> 00:27:49.320 align:middle line:84%
We can think about it, but
all of us here, none of us

00:27:49.320 --> 00:27:51.640 align:middle line:84%
is that weak to
escape, to run away.

00:27:51.640 --> 00:27:53.310 align:middle line:90%
We are all here, very strong.

00:27:53.310 --> 00:27:58.310 align:middle line:90%


00:27:58.310 --> 00:27:59.840 align:middle line:90%
And none of it is personal.

00:27:59.840 --> 00:28:02.240 align:middle line:84%
I'm not talking to a
personal individual.

00:28:02.240 --> 00:28:05.510 align:middle line:84%
We are talking about states of
consciousness, states of mind,

00:28:05.510 --> 00:28:07.040 align:middle line:90%
states of unconscious mind.

00:28:07.040 --> 00:28:10.980 align:middle line:90%


00:28:10.980 --> 00:28:13.380 align:middle line:84%
And when we are in
a group, when we

00:28:13.380 --> 00:28:14.970 align:middle line:84%
are in a collective
village like this,

00:28:14.970 --> 00:28:20.070 align:middle line:84%
it's our dharma,
our duty, to not

00:28:20.070 --> 00:28:25.290 align:middle line:84%
engage in the downward
progression of somebody.

00:28:25.290 --> 00:28:26.520 align:middle line:90%
Do you understand?

00:28:26.520 --> 00:28:29.710 align:middle line:90%
Sympathy is not compassion.

00:28:29.710 --> 00:28:33.960 align:middle line:84%
Sympathy just adds
to the pain body.

00:28:33.960 --> 00:28:35.760 align:middle line:90%
Do you comprehend?

00:28:35.760 --> 00:28:39.300 align:middle line:84%
Pity and sympathy are a
degradation of human spirit.

00:28:39.300 --> 00:28:41.610 align:middle line:84%
When you pity somebody,
you degrade them.

00:28:41.610 --> 00:28:43.710 align:middle line:90%
You take away their dignity.

00:28:43.710 --> 00:28:46.530 align:middle line:84%
When you sympathize,
you join their misery.

00:28:46.530 --> 00:28:48.810 align:middle line:90%
It expands.

00:28:48.810 --> 00:28:51.540 align:middle line:84%
And that's where most
humanity hovers around.

00:28:51.540 --> 00:28:52.350 align:middle line:90%
Pity and sympathy?

00:28:52.350 --> 00:28:53.040 align:middle line:90%
Oh, yeah.

00:28:53.040 --> 00:28:54.290 align:middle line:90%
Because so that we can belong.

00:28:54.290 --> 00:28:59.800 align:middle line:90%


00:28:59.800 --> 00:29:03.260 align:middle line:84%
Compassion might not seem
sometimes gentle or kind.

00:29:03.260 --> 00:29:06.340 align:middle line:90%
It goes much deeper.

00:29:06.340 --> 00:29:10.810 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes it will express
itself as fire, very abrupt.

00:29:10.810 --> 00:29:14.670 align:middle line:90%


00:29:14.670 --> 00:29:17.080 align:middle line:84%
So it's our duty when
we are in a group

00:29:17.080 --> 00:29:22.650 align:middle line:84%
and in a journey
like this to be aware

00:29:22.650 --> 00:29:24.780 align:middle line:90%
that we are here to evolve.

00:29:24.780 --> 00:29:27.540 align:middle line:84%
And if somebody is
stuck in an altered

00:29:27.540 --> 00:29:30.300 align:middle line:84%
or a downward progression
of consciousness,

00:29:30.300 --> 00:29:33.945 align:middle line:84%
that you serve that individual,
that we serve that individual.

00:29:33.945 --> 00:29:34.820 align:middle line:90%
Do you hear me, Ryan?

00:29:34.820 --> 00:29:37.920 align:middle line:90%


00:29:37.920 --> 00:29:39.630 align:middle line:84%
To help or serve
that person who is

00:29:39.630 --> 00:29:41.400 align:middle line:84%
stuck in that state
of consciousness

00:29:41.400 --> 00:29:43.380 align:middle line:84%
to come out of it,
because that's what

00:29:43.380 --> 00:29:45.360 align:middle line:90%
we are here all together for.

00:29:45.360 --> 00:29:51.740 align:middle line:90%


00:29:51.740 --> 00:29:53.570 align:middle line:90%
Do you hear me?

00:29:53.570 --> 00:29:56.480 align:middle line:84%
Otherwise, three people
here or two people there,

00:29:56.480 --> 00:29:58.640 align:middle line:84%
and then they're talking
about those people there.

00:29:58.640 --> 00:30:00.200 align:middle line:84%
And energetically,
you can sense it.

