00:30:45.680 --> 00:30:48.410 align:middle line:84%
It's our responsibility
not only to ourselves,

00:30:48.410 --> 00:30:51.140 align:middle line:90%
but each and every one.

00:30:51.140 --> 00:30:53.690 align:middle line:84%
Don't underestimate
how deeply you

00:30:53.690 --> 00:31:00.650 align:middle line:84%
